1934;;I Am a Thief;;American;;Robert Florey;;Mary Astor, Ricardo Cortez, Dudley Digges;;drama, crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/I_Am_a_Thief;;Ricardo Cortez plays a jewel dealer who hopes to provoke, and catch, an international jewel thief, so he transports the famous Karenina diamonds from Paris across Europe to Istanbul on the Orient Express, along with a trainload of suspicious characters.